here is a glance at west germanys 
proposed treaty for full political unification with east germany 
which would follow the july 1 merger of the two nations economies 
the political treaty is conditional on the successful resolution 
of talks between the two germanys and the four world war ii victors 
the soviet union united states britain and france on the 
international ramifications of german unity 
the parliaments of both german states would have to approve the 
proposed treaty which contains three articles of union 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
article 1 one day after joint elections are held on an 
unspecified date in december east germany will approve a clause in 
the west german constitution that will allow it to become a part of 
west germany 
