<TEXT>
article 2 the territory now known as east germany will become 
five states of a united germany brandenburg mecklenburgwest 
pomerania saxony saxonyanhalt and thuringia 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
article 3 germans in both parts of germany will form a united 
nation 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
