reference to the use of violence as a tool in the black struggle 
against south africas racist system he said those who care to 
worry about violence in our country as we do should look not at 
blacks who are denied full rights but at whites steeped in the 
ideology of racism 
but the issue of violence remained a point of disagreement after 
