<TEXT>
oconnor 
we think the supreme court of idaho properly focused on the 
presumptive unreliability of the outofcourt statements and on the 
suggestive manner in which the pediatrician conducted the 
interview 
viewing the totality of the circumstances surrounding the 
younger daughters responses to the doctors questions we find 
