under fire several times 
the six priests and educators their housekeeper and her 
15yearold daughter were roused from their sleep before dawn nov 
16 and killed by troops of the elite atlacatl infantry battalion 
two of three lieutenants leading the death squad said benavides 
issued an order to kill the priests 
the investigation has moved slowly and there have been reports 
that crucial evidence has been destroyed that military witnesses 
have been given assignments abroad to keep them from testifying 
