university and one of the regions most respected educators was 
one of those slain 
the murders provoked an international outcry and calls from some 
quarters in the us congress for sharp cuts in aid to el salvador 
the largest recipient of us aid in the hemisphere washington 
currently sends el salvador about 1 million a day in economic and 
military aid 
the money keeps this small nation and its powerful military 
afloat cristiani has taken pains to assure us officials there 
will be a goodfaith investigation and punishment of those 
responsible 
at least 72000 people have died in the civil war most of them 
civilians 
