very tired man 
this zoo has been enormously difficult to build it has taxed 
me in every imaginable way it has taken every ounce of energy ive 
had says maple 43 
willie b probably does not appreciate the effort though he has 
benefited the popular lowland gorilla named after former atlanta 
mayor william b hartsfield lived alone in a cage for 27 years 
